snippet.title: Backrooms Media - Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Get a fresh look at Backrooms Media, the upcoming VHS tape-inspired online co-op horror game that features proximity voice chat and a level editor. It will be released in Steam Early Access for PC on September 10. Wishlist it if you're interested: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2714970/Backrooms_Media/

#IGN #Gaming
